      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six. This powerplant utilizes its sequential forced induction system to deliver linear torque across the powerband, mated to the highly sought-after Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains rigid, supported by a factory double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for precise power delivery. Recent service includes a new timing belt, water pump, and a refresh of the high-pressure fuel system. While the paint exhibits minor road patina, the compression ratios remain consistent across all six cylinders, and the synchromesh engagement is crisp. This is a driver-focused example of A80 engineering, maintaining its original aerodynamic profile and factory-spec four-piston braking system.",
