      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2014 Porsche Cayman finished in Agate Grey Metallic with a Black leather interior. As a detail-oriented owner, I have ensured this vehicle has been kept in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively by certified specialists. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster and has been treated with a high-quality sealant; while it presents beautifully, there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small hairline scratch near the rear wheel arch, typical of a well-loved driver's car. The interior is smoke-free and remarkably clean. The leather seats have been regularly conditioned to prevent cracking, though there is some light softening on the driver-side bolster. All cabin electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, this Cayman is robust. I possess a comprehensive service history folder, including a recent 40,000-mile major service which",
